{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/EmptyView\/font(_:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"nonisolated"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"font"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"_"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"font"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Font","text":"Font","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4FontV"},{"kind":"text","text":"?) -> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","text":"View","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP"},{"kind":"text","text":"\n"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default font to use in this view."}]}],"name":"font"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"return-value","text":"Return Value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A view with the default font set to the value you supply."}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"font(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" to apply a specific font to all of the text in a view."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The example below shows the effects of applying fonts to individual","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"views and to view hierarchies. Font information flows down the view","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"hierarchy as part of the environment, and remains in effect unless","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"overridden at the level of an individual view or view container.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Here, the outermost "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/VStack"},{"type":"text","text":" applies a 16-point system font as a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"default font to views contained in that "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/VStack"},{"type":"text","text":". Inside that stack,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the example applies a "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Font\/largeTitle"},{"type":"text","text":" font to just the first text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view; this explicitly overrides the default. The remaining stack and the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"views contained with it continue to use the 16-point system font set by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"their containing view:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["VStack {","    Text(\"Font applied to a text view.\")","        .font(.largeTitle)","","    VStack {","        Text(\"These 2 text views have the same font\")","        Text(\"applied to their parent hierarchy\")","    }","}",".font(.system(size: 16, weight: .light, design: .default))"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/emptyview\/font(_:)"]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the default font for text in this view."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/